INSTALL for IFOS2D
==================

A detailed installation instruction is provided in the chapter 5 of the 
documentation (IFOS/doc/manual_IFOS.pdf). If the manual is not compiled,
please use the script IFOS/doc/compile_LaTeX_manual.sh

To compile IFOS2D a MAKEFILE is available in the IFOS/par directory. To
use the MAKEFILE type

make

in the IFOS/par directory. The MAKEFILE compiles the additional libaries

lib cseife
lib stfinv
lib aff
lib fourier

before compiling the main program IFOS.

-------------------------------------------

There are several known dependencies:

- GCC / ICC
- OpenMPI / Intel MPF
- fftw3
- stdc++
- math library (libm.a)

-------------------------------------------

Systems/environments the code was already successfully build on:

- Linux 2.6.31.14-0.6-desktop x86_64 
- MacOSX 10.11.1 with OpenMPI 1.10.0 and gcc-Version 5.1.0

-------------------------------------------